		"description": "<p>As your power stems from your inherent aberrancy and force of personality, you must choose Charisma as your spellcasting ability for this class. In addition, when you choose your @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-class-features.Item.9m8p73ihwnicm2zi]{Pact Boon} at 3rd level, you can only choose from @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-class-features.Item.6co2rqjh9npjg3eb]{Pact of the Blade} or @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-class-features.Item.2dp9b4a11fuxjwbc]{Pact of the Tome}, with the following alterations:</p><p><strong>Pact of the Blade.</strong> When you summon your pact weapon it is infused into one of your hands and cannot be disarmed or removed until you dismiss it.</p><p><strong>Pact of the Tome.</strong> You do not have a physical Book of Shadows but otherwise gain the benefits of this pact boon.</p>",
